# Client Package (@client) Key Info

- **Framework**: React with Vite ([main.tsx](mdc:packages/client/src/main.tsx), [App.tsx](mdc:packages/client/src/App.tsx))
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS ([tailwind.config.js](mdc:packages/client/tailwind.config.js))
- **UI Components**: `shadcn/ui` ([components.json](mdc:packages/client/components.json))
  - Components are typically added to [src/components/ui](mdc:packages/client/src/components/ui)
  - Utilities: [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:packages/client/src/lib/utils.ts)
- **Theme**: Neo-brutalism (from tweakcn.com)
  - CSS variables defined in [src/index.css](mdc:packages/client/src/index.css)
- **Routing**: `react-router-dom` used in [main.tsx](mdc:packages/client/src/main.tsx)
  - New UI at `/`, legacy UI at `/legacy` ([LegacyApp.tsx](mdc:packages/client/src/LegacyApp.tsx))
- **Path Alias**: `@/*` maps to `src/*` (see [tsconfig.json](mdc:packages/client/tsconfig.json), [vite.config.ts](mdc:packages/client/vite.config.ts))
- **Primary Goal**: Redesigning UI based on [prompt--initial-ui-designs](mdc:scratchpad/prompt--initial-ui-designs)
